  "text": "Other issues that need to be considered in creating discipline and regulations are culture and gender. Studies have shown a relationship between gender and students' behavior in the classroom, and boys have been reported to have a more destructive behavior than the girls. Studies have also indicated that the teachers' behavior in coping with students is different depending on their gender, and boys receive more negative feedback than the girls from their teachers [CITATION_1] .",
